---
title: Creamy Pesto Chicken Breast Pasta with Peas, Spinach and Cheese
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Creamy Pesto Chicken Breast Pasta in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
